{"word":"ὑπαντάω","slug":"ὑπαντάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπαντάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπό\">ὑπό</a></el>, and akin to <el>ἄντα</el> ‘over against, face-to-face’] ‘draw up close for encounter’, <b>meet<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in a friendly manner (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> with a request) <b><a href='B:470 28:9'>Mt 28:9</a>; <a href='B:490 8:27'>Lk 8:27</a>; <a href='B:490 17:12'>17:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:500 4:51'>J 4:51</a>; <a href='B:500 11:20'>11:20</a>, <a href='B:500 11:30'>30</a>; <a href='B:500 12:18'>12:18</a>;</b> non-belligerently <b><a href='B:470 8:28'>Mt 8:28</a>; <a href='B:480 5:2'>Mk 5:2</a>; <a href='B:510 16:16'>Ac 16:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in military fashion <b><a href='B:490 14:31'>Lk 14:31</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὕπανδρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπάντησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}